id Period (750\u2013868)===\n\n{| width=90% class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|- style=\"background:#cccccc\"\n|-\n! #\n! Governor\n! Start\n! End\n! Period\n! Governor Title\n! Fate\n|-\n| 1\n| [[Salih ibn Ali ibn Abdallah ibn al-Abbas]]\n| 750\n| 751\n| 1 year\n| Wali\n| Became the wali of [[Palestine (region)|Palestine]]\n|-\n| 2\n| [[Abu Awn Abd al-Malik ibn Yazid]]\n| 751\n| 753\n| 2 years\n| Wali\n| Ran away after an epidemic\n|-\n| 3\n| [[Salih ibn Ali ibn Abdallah ibn al-Abbas]]\n| 753\n| 755\n| 2 years\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 4\n| [[Abu Awn Abd al-Malik ibn Yazid]]\n| 755\n| 758\n| 3 years\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 5\n| [[Musa ibn Ka'b al-Tamimi]]\n| 758\n| 759\n| 1 year\n| Wali\n| Died\n|-\n| 6\n| [[Muhammad ibn al-Ash'ath al-Khuza'i]]\n| 759\n| 760\n| 1 year\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 7\n| [[Humayd ibn Qahtaba]]\n| 760\n| 762\n| 2 years\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 8\n| [[Yazid ibn Hatim al-Muhallabi]]\n| 762\n| 769\n| 8 years\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 9\n| [[Abdallah ibn Abd al-Rahman ibn Mu'awiya ibn Hudayj al-Tujibi]]\n| 769\n| 772\n| 4 years\n| Wali\n| -\n|-\n| 10\n| [[Muhammad ibn Abd al-Rahman ibn Mu'awiya ibn Hudayj al-Tujibi]]\n| 772\n| 772\n| 8 months\n| Wali\n| Died\n|-\n| 11\n| [[Musa ibn Ali ibn Rabah al-Lakhmi]]\n| 772\n| 778\n| 6 years\n| Wali\n| -\n|-\n| 12\n| [[Isa ibn Luqman]]\n| 778\n| 779\n| 4 months\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 13\n| [[Wadih (governor of Egypt, 779)|Wadih]]\n| 779\n| 779\n| 4 months\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 14\n| [[Mansur ibn Yazid ibn Mansur]]\n| 779\n| 779\n| 2 months\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 15\n| [[Yahya ibn Sa'id al-Harashi]]\n| 779\n| 780\n| 1 year\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 16\n| [[Salim ibn Sawada al-Tamimi]]\n| 780\n| 781\n| 1 year\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 17\n| [[Ibrahim ibn Salih|Ibrahim ibn Salih ibn Abdallah ibn al-Abbas]]\n| 781\n| 784\n| 3 years\n| Wali\n| Unseated\n|-\n| 18\n| [[Musa ibn Mus'ab al-Khath'ami]]\n| 784\n| 785\n| 1 year\n| Wali\n| Killed\n|-\n| 19\n| [[Asama ibn Amr]]\