haykh al-Mahmudi|Al-Mu'ayyad Shaykh al-Mahmudi]]\n| 1412\n| 1421\n| Sultan\n| Died\n|-\n| 7\n| [[Al-Muzaffar Ahmad|al-Muzafar Abu al-Saadat Ahmad]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\" | 1421\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned\n|-\n| 8\n| [[Sayf ad-Din Tatar|Al-Zahir Sayf-ad-Din Tatar]]\n| Sultan\n| Died\n|-\n| 9\n| [[An-Nasir ad-Din Muhammad|as-Salih Nasir-ad-Din Muhammad]]\n| 1421\n| 1422\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned\n|-\n| 10\n| [[Barsbay]]\n| 1421\n| 1438\n| Sultan\n| Died\n|-\n| 11\n| [[Al-Aziz Jamal ad-Din Yusuf|Jamal ad-Din Yusuf]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | 1438\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned\n|-\n| 12\n| [[Sayf ad-Din Jaqmaq|Jaqmaq]]\n| 1438\n| 1453\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned\n|-\n| 13\n| [[Fakhr-ad-Din Uthman]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | 1453\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned\n|-\n| 14\n| [[Sayf ad-Din Inal|Inal]]\n| 1453\n| 1460\n| Sultan\n| Resigned due to illness and died\n|-\n| 15\n| [[Al-Mu'ayyad Shihab al-Din Ahmad|al-Mu'aid Shihab ud-Din Ahmed]]\n| 1460\n| 1461\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned\n|-\n| 16\n| [[Sayf ad-Din Khushqadam|Khushqadam]]\n| 1461\n| 1467\n| Sultan\n| Died\n|-\n| 17\n| [[Sayf ad-Din Bilbay|Bilbay]]\n| 1467\n| 1467\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned and died in custody\n|-\n| 18\n| [[Timurbugha]]\n| 1467\n| 1468\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned\n|-\n| 19\n| al-Ashraf [[Qaitbay]]\n| 1468\n| 1496\n| Sultan\n| Abdicated to his son\n|-\n| 20\n| [[An-Nasir Muhammad ibn Qaitbay|al-Nasir Abu al-Sa'adat Muhammad]] ''1st reign''\n| 1496\n| 1497\n| Sultan\n| Deposed\n|-\n| 21\n| {{ill|Qansuh Khumsama'ah|arz|\u0642\u0627\u0646\u0635\u0648\u0647 \u062e\u0645\u0633\u0645\u0626\u0647}}\n| colspan=\"2\" | 1497\n| Sultan\n| Escaped and disappeared\n|-\n| 20\n| [[An-Nasir Muhammad ibn Qaitbay|al-Nasir Abu al-Sa'adat Muhammad]] ''2nd reign''\n| 1497\n| 1498\n| Sultan\n| Assassinated\n|-\n| 22\n| [[Abu Sa'id Qansuh|az-Zahir Qansuh al-Ashrafi]]\n| 1498\n| 1500\n| Sultan\n| Abdicated\n|-\n| 23\n| [[al-Ashraf Janbalat]]\n| 1500\n| 1501\n| Sultan\n| Dethroned\n|-\n| 24\n| [[Tuman bay I]]\n| 1501\n| 1501\n| Sultan\n| Deposed and executed\n|-\n| 2